title: Nightflyers Episode 3 "The Abyss Stares Back" Breakdown!
author: Think Story
comment: I totally thought Suczek was going to shoot Eris thinking he was a projection! Excited to see what happens next ep!
this show is starting to feel like a doctor who / black mirror mashup haha
I've been enjoying the show, thanks for doing these!
You gotta check out Gerald’s Game on nextflix and do a in-depth commentary. It’s based on a Steven King novel! It’s brilliant!!!

It seems like if you’re playing a character in a George R.R. Martin story you better have another gig lined up, because someone or something is going to Merc your ass before the show ends. Great video T.S., very entertaining!
description:
I break down episode 3 of George R.R. Martin's Netflix adaptation of "Nightflyers", "The Abyss Stares Back" as well as look at different theories and details you missed!
